    },
    {
      "participant_id": "grace",
      "text": "That's great. Can you give me an example of how you've handled a production incident?",
      "start_time": "2024-01-15T14:01:36",
      "end_time": "2024-01-15T14:01:46",
      "is_question": true
    },
    {
      "participant_id": "eve",
      "text": "Last month, we had a critical database outage during peak traffic. I led the incident response, coordinated with the DBA team, and we restored service within 15 minutes. Afterward, I implemented better monitoring and failover mechanisms.",
      "start_time": "2024-01-15T14:01:54",
      "end_time": "2024-01-15T14:02:04",
      "is_question": false
    },
    {
      "participant_id": "frank",
      "text": "Excellent. How do you approach system design for high availability?",
      "start_time": "2024-01-15T14:02:12",
      "end_time": "2024-01-15T14:02:22",
      "is_question": true
    },
    {
      "participant_id": "eve",
      "text": "I focus on redundancy, circuit breakers, and graceful degradation. I also believe in chaos engineering - regularly testing failure scenarios in staging environments.",
      "start_time": "2024-01-15T14:02:30",
      "end_time": "2024-01-15T14:02:40",
      "is_question": false
